## ⚖️ **Challenges & Opposition**

⚠️ **Targeted by the U.S. Government** – Placed on the **FBI’s Most Wanted List** in 1970.  
⚠️ **Criticized for Communist Ties** – Lost teaching positions due to **her Marxist politics**.  
⚠️ **Controversial in Mainstream Feminism** – Rejected by some white feminists for **prioritizing racial issues**.

